    "class": "name"
   },
   "html": "\n[ すぎやま・はじめ ]"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "prof"
   },
   "html": "\n陸相、参謀総長、教育総監、陸軍次官、軍務局長、航空本部長、航空課長、元帥陸軍大将"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "table",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "lt"
   },
   "html": "<tbody><tr><td class=\"lt\"><a href=\"03s.html\">一覧　（サ）</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td><td class=\"lt\"><a href.html\"=\"\">　</a></td></tr></tbody>"
  },
  {
   "type": "raw",
   "tag": "div",
   "attrs": {
    "class": "off"
   },
   "html": "<span class=\"m_r\">エピソード 1</span>調査中。"
  },
  {
   "type": "timeline",
   "rows": [
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　福岡県出身。陸士卒。陸大卒。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　満州事変開始時の陸軍次官、<a href=\"../1936/02226ji.html\">二・二六事件</a>時の参謀次長。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　教育総監を経て、<a href=\"../1937/haya_1.html\">林内閣</a>の陸相に就任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　続く<a href=\"../1937/kono1_1.html\">近衛内閣①</a>に留任し、<a href=\"../1937/07rokok.html\">盧溝橋事件</a>では強硬論を主張。日中戦争を全面戦争化させた。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　その後、参謀総長として<a href=\"../1941/07futu2.html\">南部仏印進駐</a>、<a href=\"../1941/12hawai.html\">太平洋戦争開戦</a>などを推進。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../p/thideki.html\">東條首相兼陸相</a>の<a href=\"../1944/02kenni.html\">参謀総長兼任</a>の際、辞任し教育総監に再任。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1944/koiso_1.html\">小磯内閣</a>で再び陸相。総辞職後、第一総軍司令官。"
      }
     ]
    },
    {
     "cls": "",
     "cells": [
      {
       "id": null,
       "cls": "hist",
       "html": "\n・　<a href=\"../1945/08gyoku.html\">敗戦</a>を迎え自決。"
      }
     ]
    }
   ]
  },
